      {
        "number": 11,
        "name": "MAURICIO",
        "highlights": "Paraguay's standout attacker. Scored consolation goal at 72' with composed left-foot finish. Most threatening forward with 4 shots and direct running at USA's defence."
      },
      {
        "number": 10,
        "name": "Julio ENCISO",
        "highlights": "Fastest player on pitch at 33.3 km/h. Dangerous in transition with pace behind USA's defensive line. Key outlet for Paraguay's counter-attacks despite limited possession."
      },
